    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use this protocol to manage scale and contents for a layer hosted in a view. When a window changes its backing resolution, AppKit attempts to automatically update the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "contentsScale"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "contents"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of all "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "CALayer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " objects in the window to match the new resolution. Layers backed by a view are updated automatically. Any layer whose "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "contents"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property is set to an "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSImage"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object is also updated automatically. Based on the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSImage"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object’s available representations, AppKit selects an appropriate bitmapped representation, or rasterizes a resolution-independent representation at the appropriate scale factor.  "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For all other layers, AppKit checks whether the layer has a delegate that implements this protocol.  If so, AppKit asks the layer's delegate whether it should automatically update the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "contentsScale"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " for that layer to match the new scale factor of the window."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
